song.title: K.K. Love Song (Mangled Melody Remix)
song.info:
Began as a remix of "K.K. Love Song" from Animal Crossing (Gamecube). I couldn't quite figure out the melody and it never really got off the ground.
From the album release "Test Patterns", more info and download: http://nwserver.ath.cx/nwserver/2011/12/04/hornpipe2-test-patterns/
